title: 'Config: default notification target for proactive outreach'
---
Heartbeat (T007) and any other proactive agent behavior needs to know where to send unsolicited messages. Add a notify config section (or per-channel field) specifying the default outbound target: e.g. telegram.notify_chat_id, or a channel-agnostic notify_target with channel + address. Without this, heartbeat can reason but cannot reach the user.